Ishikari Nabe

Konbu 5 cm
2 slices of salmon
Chinese cabbage 3 leaves
Crowndaisy 100g
2 shiitake mushrooms
Leek
Cotton tofu 150g
Miso 50g
2 tbsp sake
2 tbsp mirin
2 tbsp soy sauce
Salted butter 20g


Bring kelp to a boil and remove
Add miso, sake, mirin, soy
bring to a boil
add ingredients
cook
add butter
eat

Show Konbu
Show Sake
Show Mirin
Show Miso
Slice Shiitake with cross
Slice Napa
Slice Leek
Chop Greens
Cut tofu
Cut Salmon

Konbu in pot
Add 1L water
Bring to Boil
Remove konbu
reduce to medium
Add sake
	mirin
	soy
	miso
Add Veg
Cook until Tender
Add Salmon
Cook until done
Add butter
Serve